Evaluation Toolkit for A2D Dataset
Authors: Chenliang Xu and Jason J. Corso
Email: {cliangxu,jjcorso}@umich.edu
Date: 06/01/2015
Version: 1.0

We provide evaluation code for pixel-level actor-action semantic segmentation and ground truth labels for video-level actor-action single- and multiple-label recognition.

----------------------------------------
Pixel-level Actor-Action Semantic Segmentation

See evalSegmentation.m for detail.

----------------------------------------
Video-level Actor-Action Single- and Multiple-Label Recognition

AR.mat
    vid - 11 digit vid ID
    test - a flag to denote test (1) or train (0)
    single - ground truth single label for videos
    multiple - ground truth multiple labels for videos

We follow THUMOS Challenge 2014 to compute mAP for multiple label evaluation.
See http://crcv.ucf.edu/THUMOS14/home.html


